		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It sounds like mofifying tecmo bowl to detect turbo might be difficult.  Maybe it would be easier to standardize your league onto one specific emulator, and modify that emulator to detect turbo.  You'd probably need to have the emulators detect modifications to themselves as well, as is common with many networked games.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


